question that comes up.

00:53:12.290 --> 00:53:19.215
So just a lot of totally
unfocused reading

00:53:19.215 --> 00:53:22.460
of Wikipedia or
weird papers ends up

00:53:22.460 --> 00:53:23.789
coming in handy later on.

