I'm looking for,

00:54:05.790 --> 00:54:07.940
that has a higher hit rate
than any of the specialized

00:54:07.940 --> 00:54:08.460
services.

00:54:08.460 --> 00:54:10.580
So I appreciate that.

00:54:10.580 --> 00:54:11.780
AUDIENCE: Cool, thank you.

00:54:11.780 --> 00:54:14.620
RANDALL MUNROE: Thank you.

00:54:14.620 --> 00:54:17.840
AUDIENCE: Hi, so you had
a lot of fans show up.

00:54:17.840 --> 00:54:21.230
And that's just
to hear you talk.

00:54:21.230 --> 00:54:24.495
You must get a bunch of
requests on the email address

00:54:24.495 --> 00:54:27.400
